OL,6,GWhat does the future hold for
OL,7,GNewsnight?
OL,9,FIt has been reported that the budget
OL,10,Ffaces a massive cut and that the
OL,11,Fformat may change. So far nothing has
OL,12,Fbeen confirmed.
OL,14,FBut given the BBC's financial
OL,15,Fsituation and the programme's low
OL,16,Fviewing figures, it is inevitable
OL,17,Fthat questions will be asked about
OL,18,Fwhether Newsnight in its current form
OL,19,Frepresents value for money.
OL,3,CNewsnight: a move to BBC One is worth
OL,4,Cconsidering
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/7
