OL,6,FAt its best Newsnight offers informed
OL,7,Fdiscussion, probing interviews,
OL,8,Fanalysis and original journalism.
OL,10,FBut it seems to have lost any sense
OL,11,Fof being must-see viewing ` a
OL,12,Fprogramme which opinion formers and
OL,13,Fnews junkies feel is essential to
OL,14,Ftheir day.
OL,16,FIt is hard to quite decide where this
OL,17,Fdecline stems from.
OL,19,FOf course, competition has increased
OL,20,Fand linear viewing is in decline.
OL,3,CNewsnight: a move to BBC One is worth
OL,4,Cconsidering
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/7
