OL,6,FI would personally argue that
OL,7,FNewsnight suffered some damage after
OL,8,Fthe main BBC One news moved to 10pm
OL,9,Fin 2000.
OL,11,FIt was always a big ask to expect
OL,12,Fviewers to switch over straight away
OL,13,Ffor yet more news.
OL,15,FNow BBC News viewers face the dilemma
OL,16,Fbetween staying for the regional news
OL,17,For switching to Newsnight's top story.
OL,3,CNewsnight: a move to BBC One is worth
OL,4,Cconsidering
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/7
