OL,6,FIt is worth noting that the programme
OL,7,Fmounted a full recovery from the
OL,8,Ffallout over the Jimmy Savile scandal
OL,9,Fand a subsequent flawed investigation
OL,10,Finto alleged child abuse. The credit
OL,11,Ffor that should go to Ian Katz who is
OL,12,Fnow with Channel 4.
OL,14,FBut whatever might happen to
OL,15,FNewsnight, the loss of a daily forum
OL,16,Ffor analysis and informed discussion
OL,17,Fon a major BBC channel should surely
OL,18,Fbe considered unthinkable.
OL,20,FHere's a radical suggestion. Move an
OL,21,Fevolved Newsnight on to BBC One.
OL,3,CNewsnight: a move to BBC One is worth
OL,4,Cconsidering
