OL,6,FThis is not as daft as it sounds.
OL,8,FFirstly, the programme's forefathers
OL,9,F` 24 Hours, Midweek and the late-70s
OL,10,Fprogramme titled Tonight ` were all
OL,11,Fon BBC One.
OL,13,FThe move of the daily current affairs
OL,14,Fprogramme to BBC Two in 1980 was
OL,15,Fcontroversial at the time but soon
OL,16,Fseemed to make sense.
OL,18,FBut in recent years, BBC One has
OL,19,Fstruggled to fill the late evenings `
OL,20,Fthe time is often simply filled by
OL,21,Frepeats as a result of budget cuts.
OL,3,CNewsnight: a move to BBC One is worth
OL,4,Cconsidering
