OL,6,FA restyled Newsnight ` with a very
OL,7,Ftight focus on interviews and
OL,8,Fanalysis to complement the Ten `
OL,9,Fcould run on BBC One at 10.40pm.
OL,11,FIt would naturally inherit some of
OL,12,Fthe Ten's viewers.
OL,14,FOf course, it could only run three
OL,15,Fdays a week normally ` Thursdays
OL,16,Fbelong to Question Time and it would
OL,17,Fbe folly to suggest ditching Graham
OL,18,FNorton on Fridays for something so
OL,19,Fvery different.
OL,3,CNewsnight: a move to BBC One is worth
OL,4,Cconsidering
