OL,6,FYes, the new Newsnight would be
OL,7,Fcheaper. But with a bigger audience
OL,8,Fit could regain lost influence and
OL,9,Fprestige.
OL,11,FIt is an idea worthy of discussion.
OL,3,CNewsnight: a move to BBC One is worth
OL,4,Cconsidering
